## 10^-43 seconds -- 300 thousand years

Hot quark soup expands and cools. Universe is opaque, all photons immediately hit other particles and are absorbed.

## 300 thousand years -- 700 million years

Matter soup cools to 3000K and universe stops being opaque; radiation is emitted that can nowadays be observed as [Cosmic Microwave Background]() (CMB).

